  <title>Genetic Diversity and Pathogenicity of Xanthomonas axonopodis Strains Inducing Citrus Canker Disease in Iran and South Korea</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=adc92b823e2a874f768a817c7e6024bc&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
  <authors>
    <link title="G Khodakaramian" attr="ID=SERP,5097.1">/academic/search?q=G+Khodakaramian&amp;amp;mkt=zh-cn</link>
